'''Brad Emmerson''' is an ice sledge hockey player and Paralympic gold medalist.  Competing at the 2010 Winter Paralympics, he won a gold medal in the [[Ice sledge hockey at the 2010 Winter Paralympics|men's ice sledge hockey tournament]].<ref name=ipcrecords>{{cite web|url=http://www.paralympic.org/ipc_results/search.php?games=2010PWG&gender=all&medal=medals&npc=USA&sport=all|publisher=International Paralympic Committee|location=Germany|title=Athlete Search Results|accessdate=10 February 2010}}</ref>

